The ternary blend PSCs (ITO/ZnO/PTzBT:ITIC:PC61BM/MoOx/Ag) were fabricated with PTzBT, ITIC, and PC61BM (Fig. 1d). The ESR signals and performance of the fabricated cells were simultaneously measured for the conditions of dark or solar irradiation by AM1.5 G, 100 mW cm−2 solar simulator (OTENTOSUN-150LX). The energy-level diagram of the PTzBT cell is show in Fig. 1e, whose energy values are taken from the literatures for ZnO and MoOx (ref. 25), PTzBT and ITIC8, PC61BM26, holes of singly charged zinc interstitial (Zni+\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
